<CSS-webkit-tap-highlight-color>
<summary>
<strong><c>-webkit-tap-highlight-color</c></strong> is a non-standard CSS property that sets the color of the highlight that appears over a link while it&amp;apos;s being tapped. The highlighting indicates to the user that their tap is being successfully recognized, and indicates which element they&amp;apos;re tapping on.
</summary>
